<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Stephan von Absberg, Vogt von Abenberg, und Abenberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet, den Hermann Kraus, Armmann des Hermann Stör, Bürger zu Nürnberg, entgegen altem Herkommen nicht zu Steuer und Wache für Abenberg zu nötigen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_524" id="261v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_524_r2l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Steffan von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l3">Abſpergk 
<add><ab facs="#facs_524_line_1576348037214_3415">vogt </ab></add> vnd den <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des Rats der <expan>St<ex>at</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Abemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_524_r2l4">Lıeber her Steffan 
<del rend="strikethrough">vns </del> vnd <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freunde / Vns hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l5">fürgelegt <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Stör / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger / vvie daʒ Jr den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l6"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Krawſen bey Abemberg geſeſſen <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> Armman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l7"><expan>nöte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd dringen wolt / daʒ Er mit den ~ von <expan>Abemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l9">ſtewr vnd wache das doch von alter niht <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l10">vnd darumb ſo müſʒ er auch vor ew empflüchten gee </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l12">vnd ſey vnſicher vor ew / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr des <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l13"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Armman <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſʒen wöllet / als das von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l14">alter herkumen iſt / Vnd Jn auch ſıchert auf freuntlich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l15">recht / das wollen vvir v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> allcʒeit gern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l16"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> /vnd het 
<add><ab facs="#facs_524_line_1576348086102_3445">Jr </ab></add> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l18"> Armmans icht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / darumb 
<del rend="strikethrough">vvile </del> vvil 
<del rend="strikethrough">ew </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_524_r2l17">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſch<ex>einboten</ex></expan> etc </del></ab></add> der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l23"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger 
<add><ab facs="#facs_524_r1l1">ew oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſcheinb<ex>oten</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_524_r1l2">mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gevvalt </ab></add> von <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_524_line_1576348116967_3466"><expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> Armman </ab></add> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> ſlewnigs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l24"><expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> gern helffen <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> er des ermant vvirdt / vnd lat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l25">vns des ewr freuntlich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> vviſſen <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_524_r2l26">
<del rend="strikethrough">fe </del> in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> franciſſi </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_524" id="261v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Steffan von Abspergk, <add>vogt</add>, und den
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des rats der
                            <expan>st<ex>at</ex></expan> czu <expan>Abemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Steffan und <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freunde, uns hat
                        fürgelegt <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Stör, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        burger, wie daz ir den <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Krawsen bey Abemberg
                        gesessen, <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> armman,
                            <expan>nöte<ex>n</ex></expan> und dringen wolt, daz er mit den von
                                <expan>Abemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> stewr und wache, das doch von alter
                        niht <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, und darumb so müsz er auch vor ew
                        empflüchten gee und sey unsicher vor ew. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex>,</expan>
                        daz ir des <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> armman <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        laszen wöllet, als das von alter herkumen ist, und in auch sichert auf
                        freuntlich recht. Das wollen wir ümb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> allczeit gern
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>; und het <add>ir</add>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers armmans icht <expan>cze
                                sprech<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> darumb wil der
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger <add>ew oder
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinb<ex>oten</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt</add> von
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> armman</add>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> slewnigs
                                <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> gern helffen,
                            <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er des ermant wirdt; und lat uns des ewr
                        freuntlich, <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wissen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Francissi.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
